        "release_notes": {
            "en-US": "2013-08-02\n- Access keys have been updated\n- Plain text as default mode now works\n- Got rid of a bunch of bugs\n- AutoCopy support has been switched to <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/a4808be919211e00a9974896b1e60b4345b5a9722ab8c54cafe6beaa0f861e77/http%3A//forum.infas.net/viewforum.php%3Ff=8\">Auto Copy Plus</a>"
        },
        "reviewed": null,
